{"tid":1603483,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"諸君請聽gphone一言","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T17:18:45.000Z","uid":182843,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5bc9f8a8707a257714cd8a6e5534d08d34e8027f","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ba4XHfj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBa4XHfj.png&h=6dfcbe52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dQ0E10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dQ0E10.png&h=a849a18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班狗點會唔知被清算有幾痛？<span style=\"color: red;\">輸咗唔只要生生世世留喺大灣區，佢地嘅狗二代、狗宗十八二十代都要遺臭萬年成為千古罪人，永不翻</span><span style=\"color: red;\">生</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以佢地唔會介意大家笑佢地毅進仔，抑或老婆同人共享，因為贏咗嘅話就可以慢慢復仇！佢地先係抱住破釜沉舟嘅心態出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後琴日又有過百個手足被捕了。我地仲要承受幾多次手足畀人捉、打、姦，甚至殺嘅屈辱同悲痛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以希望大家十月一真係有晒心理準備上戰場<span style=\"color: red;\">（無錯係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戰場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民皆兵做唔做到唔緊要，但全民提升起碼一個lv得唔得？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><em>三個幾月都冇出過嚟嘅，出嚟啦<br />\n出親嚟都只係行嘅，幫下手試下做埋物資兵<br />\n企開中後排嘅，可以試下幫手做滅火/揸大聲公協調手足撤退<br />\n甚或升級做埋魔法師</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多⋯⋯<span style=\"color: orange;\">所有你諗過但無做過嘅，就喺10月1號畀次機會自己，好唔好？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核爆都唔割啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">唔係魚死就網破，一個連狗都明嘅道理，我地仲點可以無覺悟？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">諗好所有最壞打算，安排好佢，做足思想準備，唔好等到臨場先至怯。我唔知10月1係咪end game，但呢一日一定係繼71之後最大象徵意義嘅一日。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十月一 賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">May the odds be ever in your favor</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDcKntS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDcKntS.gif&h=91d00805&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e062ae1d9ecc90ba1e8b95523201384929270685","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"2c09bf7d1bcf3535499e47ea8171a5feb038103b","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"月"},{"pid":"0eb3238f1ccc5f1d398d3154ee983f1b7e161b6b","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"6099b69ae64237ef9bac1b5cf60a1b2494982bd5","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"賀"},{"pid":"261d57121da5ab814d23ea7429b4077ef4e2a53b","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"佢"},{"pid":"35dc1d92c27e567ff2d61498f9a3495687a3574d","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:01:26.000Z","msg":"老"},{"pid":"d104e81048f8d5a4319f0d19b42df5989ab25a7b","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"母"},{"pid":"f986cb54f9712f56ee8d0df86eddd5d3aeb63f3e","tid":1603483,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim